    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>3rd-level Way of Mercy feature</i></p><p>You gain proficiency in the &amp;Reference[skill=Insight] and &amp;Reference[skill=Medicine] skills, and you gain proficiency with the @item[herbalism kit|PHB].</p><p>You also gain a special mask, which you often wear when using the features of this subclass. You determine its appearance, or generate it randomly by rolling on the Merciful Mask table.</p><table class=\"w-100 rd__table  stripe-odd-table\" data-roll-name-ancestor=\"Merciful Mask\"><caption>Merciful Mask</caption><thead><tr><th class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-rd-isroller=\"true\">[[/r d6]]</th><th class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \" data-rd-isroller=\"false\">Mask Appearance</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-roll-min=\"1\" data-roll-max=\"1\">1</td><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \">Raven</td></tr><tr><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-roll-min=\"2\" data-roll-max=\"2\">2</td><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \">Blank and white</td></tr><tr><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-roll-min=\"3\" data-roll-max=\"3\">3</td><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \">Crying visage</td></tr><tr><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-roll-min=\"4\" data-roll-max=\"4\">4</td><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \">Laughing visage</td></tr><tr><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-roll-min=\"5\" data-roll-max=\"5\">5</td><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \">Skull</td></tr><tr><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-2 ve-text-center \" data-roll-min=\"6\" data-roll-max=\"6\">6</td><td class=\"rd__th ve-col-10 \">Butterfly</td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
